  [ Upstream Kernel Changes ]

  * ASoC: ABE DSP: Correct mute/unmute to manage Left/Right channels
  * OMAP4: powerdomain: Fix ABE context lost offset
  * ASoC: ABE HAL: Reset DBG and ABE IRQ FIFO pointers
  * ASoC: ABE DSP: Save/restore context based on stream activity
  * ASoC: ABE DSP: protect ABE driver against race condition with McPDM
  * ASoC: McPDM: Increase critical region for PCM ops
  * ASoC: McPDM: Update the control of the channels for SW reset
  * ASoC: ABE DSP: Use 98MHz for ABE OPP25 processing
  * ASoC: Ignore first ABE IRQ to avoid underflow at ALSA level
  * Fix border effect of local timer DVFS fix

